trans-unit.source: Represents a WSDL violation of the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles" /> object that specifies whether the Web service declares that it conforms to the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles" /> object that specifies whether the Web service declares that it conforms to the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles" />物件，指定 Web 服務是否宣告符合 WSI Basic Profile version 1.1。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that provides a detailed description of the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile.
A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that provides a detailed description of the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.String" />提供 WSDL 違反的基本設定檔的詳細的描述。

trans-unit.source: Represents WSDL elements that do not comply with the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> that contains the WSDL elements that do not comply with the WSI Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> ，其中包含不符合 WSI Basic Profile 1.1 版規格的 WSDL 項目。

trans-unit.source: Gets the identifier for the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the identifier (For example, R2038) for the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> WSDL 發生違規的 Basic Profile 1.1 版規格包含的識別項 (例如，R2038)。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.String" /> object that describes the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
The <see cref="T:System.String" /> object that describes the WSDL violation of the Basic Profile version 1.1 specification.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />描述 WSDL 違反的 Basic Profile 1.1 版規格的物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that comprises information from <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.NormativeStatement" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Details" />, and <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Elements" />.

A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that comprises information from <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.NormativeStatement" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Details" />, and <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation.Elements" />.
